name: TeenyUbloxConnect
description: Library for serial communication with u-blox GNSS modules.  Derived from SparkFun_u-blox_GNSS_Arduino_Library but only supports UBX NAV PVT and SAT packets and packet info.  An example of a project that uses this library can be found here: https://github.com/BeakeS/TeenyGPSTestbed_C2.git
